        android:text="Version: 0.2\nDeveloped by: \n- Roni Polisanov\n- Haim Elbaz\n- Reut Leib\nPart of the Introduction to Mobile Computing Course, 2018. \nInstructors: Dr. Amnon Dekel and Amir Uval.\nÂ© 2018 - The Dept. of Software Engineering, Shenkar: Engineering. Design. Art"
